snippet.title: Cards Wars
snippet.description: Cards Wars Strategy game. Try to conquer the world using the highest sets of cards in this turn based game.

snippet.title: Tequila Zombies
snippet.description: Tequila Zombies Fighting game. Kill all zombies and earn cash to buy new weapons to stay alive as long as possible.

snippet.title: Turbo Golf
snippet.description: Turbo Golf Sports game. Try to put the golfball as fast as you can and collect coins to buy upgrades and power-ups.

snippet.title: Doodle Dino Bowl
snippet.description: Doodle Dino Bowl Let the bowling ball fly as far as possible. Collect the stars and pins to buy upgrades in the shop.

snippet.title: Knightmare Tower
snippet.description: Knightmare Tower Becom a brave knight fighting the monsters flying through the tower. Earn cash to buy upgrades.

snippet.title: Into Space 2
snippet.description: Into Space 2 Arcade game. Try to land the rocket on the moon and collect cash to upgrade and buy items.

snippet.title: Frenzy Hotel
snippet.description: Frenzy Hotel Management game. Help the customers of the hotel to make money and buy new stuff.

snippet.title: Touch The Sky
snippet.description: Touch The Sky Arcade game. Tr to fly as far as you can and earn candy to buy upgrades to fly even further.

snippet.title: GARE: Sapphire Mechs
snippet.description: GARE: Sapphire Mechs Shooting game. End the war on the Vitris 47 planet controlling a fighter mech.

snippet.title: Star Pirate: Inception
snippet.description: Star Pirate: Inception Space shooter. Shoot and collect your way through over 12 very exciting missions in the universe.
